OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fsettled evening with light winds,
OL,7,FOrkney seeing the best of the late
OL,8,Fsunny periods. The rest of the night
OL,9,Fwill be dry for most with clear spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA mostly dry and bright
OL,12,Fmorning with some hazy sunny spells.
OL,13,FTurning cloudier through the afternoon
OL,14,Ffor Orkney with the odd spot of rain,
OL,15,Fbut remaining mainly dry for Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
